description: Demolition of Mercier House, Saunders House, Knight House and Counsell House at northern end of site. Erection of a four-storey building to provide 99 affordable dwellings together with associated access and landscaping. The proposal includes the provision of 4 affordable dwellings within Beverley Gate (with the remainder of Beverley Gate providing 12 residential units).
site_name: Whitelands Park (North Part of former Whitelands Col.)
